trans-unit.source: Runs a set of child activities at the same time.
trans-unit.target: Kör en uppsättning underordnade aktiviteter på samma gång.
Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The order in which child activities are run is non-deterministic.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Ordningen i vilken underordnade aktiviteter körs är icke-deterministisk.

trans-unit.source: The ParallelActivity is a <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, which means the ParallelActivity can contain other activities.
trans-unit.target: ParallelActivity är en <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>, vilket innebär att ParallelActivity kan innehålla andra aktiviteter.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.CompositeActivity>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity> activity is the only activity that can be the child of a ParallelActivity.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity>aktivitet är den enda aktivitet som kan vara underordnad en ParallelActivity.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.SequenceActivity>

trans-unit.source: Only one activity can run at a time.
trans-unit.target: Endast en aktivitet kan köras samtidigt.

trans-unit.source: The ParallelActivity only finishes when all children are complete.
trans-unit.target: ParallelActivity slutförs bara när du är klar med alla underordnade.

trans-unit.source: The ParallelActivity is especially useful when there are one or more blocking activities, such as the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> activity, in one or more of the branches.
trans-unit.target: ParallelActivity är användbart när det finns en eller flera blockeringsaktiviteter som den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>aktivitet i en eller flera grenar.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, the ParallelActivity actually switches to a different branch when the <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity> is blocked.
trans-unit.target: I det här scenariot i ParallelActivity faktiskt växlar till en annan gren när den <xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>blockeras.</xref:System.Workflow.Activities.DelayActivity>

trans-unit.source: If there are no blocking activities in any one of the ParallelActivity branches then the activity uses a non-deterministic sequence.
trans-unit.target: Om det inte finns några blockeringsaktiviteter i en ParallelActivity förgreningar använder en icke-deterministiska sekvens med aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ParallelActivity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ParallelActivity"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ParallelActivity"></xref> class using the name of the activity.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Activities.ParallelActivity"> </xref> klassen med namnet på aktiviteten.

trans-unit.source: The user-defined name of the activity.
